The pattern mining and classification tree constraint propagators in this package
are ports of the oscar-ml module, originally authored by:
  - John Aoga (johnaoga@gmail.com)
  - Pierre Schaus

The ported code preserves the algorithmic logic and data structures from the
original Scala implementation while adapting them to Python and the CPMpy
constraint modeling framework.
